Comment: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:28.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:32.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Courage is in two worlds\Nそう Together now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:32.79,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「proof！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:35.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「それが　二つ　結ぶ絆だから」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:38.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:39.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「my dream！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「明日の扉の向こう期待しちゃう」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:43.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「alone！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,もしも月のない　空に星が輝いても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「no magic！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:56.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,もしも太陽が無い　空の雲が流れてても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,淋しそうに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:01.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,当たり前に　隣に居た
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:06.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,君を探してる二人映る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:07.41,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,『frame Decorate』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:11.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,思うがままワガまま　ありのままに並べよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,相性『Plus＋ Minus－ Multiply× Divide÷ 』by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:15.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,全部好き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Calling me Calling you (and you)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,君と歩きたい未来階段（stairs）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Lucky Lucky Shiny 二人の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:26.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ときめきDreamin'　明日晴れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:29.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,なら　万事オーライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっとブルー　Weakness「but happy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:37.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,けど君が居るから　Being saved
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:39.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,無駄な時間なんて無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,雨上がる空をWaiting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:44.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Check it out　見上げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:47.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Courage is in two worlds\Nそう Together now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「proof！」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「それが　二つ　結ぶ絆だから」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:54.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:57.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「どんな明日を照らすのかな？ スポットライト」
Comment: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:28.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:32.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,勇气两个世界都在\N所以是时候一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:32.79,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「证据」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:35.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「就是紧系你我的羁绊」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:38.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,每个人都对漂亮的少女微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:39.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「我的梦想」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.63,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「不禁期待明天之后会是怎样」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:43.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「一人」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,纵使月色淡去 繁星也能闪耀夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.02,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「无关魔法」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:56.52,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,即便太阳不在 云朵也湍流在天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,与寂寞陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:01.69,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,理所当然地 守护在彼此身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:06.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,寻找你的身音 把两人倒映
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:07.41,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,盛装点缀于画框
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:11.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,随心所欲 撒娇任性 就这原原本本地并列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,契合度是「加减乘除」的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:15.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,全都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,呼唤感召你与我（你也一样）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,想和你一同登上未来的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,幸运有趣阳光的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:26.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,怦然心动的梦境 明日肯定天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:29.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,如此万事都行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.39,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,情绪微蓝 稍怕懦弱「但很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:37.23,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,因有你在得到了救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:39.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,绝没有时间被虚度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.90,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,不过等候雨过天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:44.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,抬起头 快来看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:47.74,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,勇气两个世界都在\N所以是时候一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「证据」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「就是紧系你我的羁绊」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:54.83,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,每个人都对漂亮的少女微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:57.12,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「聚光灯下 映照的明天又能怎样」
Comment: 1,0:00:26.51,0:00:29.51,main-JP,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.26,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,風もう起きたかな
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.31,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,行ってきます
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.06,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,あっ　行ってらっしゃい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.07,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,ステージ楽しみね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.07,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,うん　頑張る
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.82,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いっぱい歌おう
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.12,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,行ってきまーす
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.96,0:01:03.96,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,来たね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.10,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,行っちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.35,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,遅刻
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.14,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ううん　大丈夫　早起きしたから
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.10,0:01:26.15,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん　ライブ見てくれるかなー
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.15,0:01:27.73,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,さあね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.73,0:01:30.82,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリィのファンだし　配信もあるもんね
Comment: 1,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.43,main-JP,,0,0,0,,main
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.06,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,誰もいないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.10,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,デッド
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.10,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,着いた
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.90,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ここでいいか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.32,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,だめだって
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リッド
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリルラ　パリルラ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.21,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,パムパムパワー
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.34,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ルルリラ　プルリラ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.01,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ポップンパーン
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.33,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,行こう あずき
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.33,0:04:31.88,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.00,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,危ないな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.47,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,ルルとリリィ初ライブだね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.59,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,楽しみ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.26,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,チケット完売だって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.68,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,すごいよね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.72,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,私ライブとか初めて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.97,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,私も
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.73,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,中学生が行っても大丈夫かな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.14,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.15,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,バスケ部の角谷くんたちも行くって言ってたし
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.65,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,あの人すごい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.03,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,熱狂的なファンだね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.41,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,格好よ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.99,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,変装完璧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.50,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,僕まで
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ほら見てうぐいす
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.75,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お客さんいっぱい来てくれてるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.21,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんか芸能人みたい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.63,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,生意気だな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.88,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃんのファンもいるけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.18,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,大きいわね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.18,0:05:25.76,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.94,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,頑張ろう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.57,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,はい　お待たせ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.44,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.90,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,いやー　まさかあの二人がユニット組むなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.07,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,すげえよな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.87,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,だな　びっくりだわ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.87,0:05:48.24,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,夢の組み合わせすぎる
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.71,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,おい　あんま騒ぐなよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.29,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,おいおい　楽しみにしてただろ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.55,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,まあ　ちょっとな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.17,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,嘘つけ　翔太ワクワクして
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.51,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,昨日寝れなかったって言ってたじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.89,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,言ってねえし
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.97,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,え　翔太くん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.56,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,で　お前はどっち
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.73,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,だからルルとリリィだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.73,0:06:16.06,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,ルルとリリィ　どっちがいいんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.90,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,やっぱりサインもらったリリィちゃんか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.94,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,いや　俺は
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.99,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,じゃあ大人っぽいルルちゃんの方がいいってことか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.37,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,だから　そ　その
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.58,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,どっちなんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.16,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,うそ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.62,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,ル　ル
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.54,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,応援よろしく
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.13,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,ルルルルルルル
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.51,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,やばい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.10,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.77,main-JP,Staff 1,0,0,0,,リリィさん　よろしくお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.56,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.27,main-JP,Staff 2/3,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.82,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,おはようリリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.24,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.66,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,調子はどう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.95,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ばっちりです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.95,0:07:09.74,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,いいねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.75,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あ社長　招待局のリストを見てくれた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.75,0:07:17.00,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,おー チェックしたよ　後で挨拶回っとく
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.13,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ルルは
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.38,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,もう控室に入ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.34,main-JP,Staff 4,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.93,main-JP,Staff 4,0,0,0,,トロッコですけど　あれ本当にやります
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.64,main-JP,Staff 5,0,0,0,,今日客席いっぱいで通れないんですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.60,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,そこを何とか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.31,main-JP,Staff 4,0,0,0,,まぁ　なんかやり方考えてみますけど
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.64,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,お願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.56,main-JP,Staff 5,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.86,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,まぁ 無理あるよね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,わあ かわいい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.94,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お菓子ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.57,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん　マカロン　食べてみたかったな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.74,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.70,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,緊張してきました
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.96,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,一緒に食べよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.96,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,きっとおいしいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.22,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,かわいい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.18,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いただきます
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.93,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,これ　社長の差し入れらしいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.72,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,えっ意外です
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.98,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おいしいねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.39,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,おいしいです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.98,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ちょっと緊張解けた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.73,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい　笑えるようになりました
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.36,0:08:29.41,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,さっきまで　ほっぺた引きつってて変顔になりそうで
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.70,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃんの変顔見たいな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.41,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,こんな感じです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.67,0:08:42.50,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いつも通りにやれば大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.55,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リラックスリラックス
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.51,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.02,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,この歌って
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.06,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,二人とも　準備できた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.77,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,今行きます
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.03,main-JP,Staff 3,0,0,0,,まもなく開演です
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.66,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おー　人いっぱい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.95,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,満員ですね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.54,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,すごいすごい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.54,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,こんな大勢の前で
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.96,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あとは目いっぱいやるだけだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.34,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ここまで頑張ってきたんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.34,0:09:25.96,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.46,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,よーし
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.17,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ぶちかます
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.47,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,その調子
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.01,0:09:34.80,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ルル
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.76,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,いい歌声だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.39,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,自信持って
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.56,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.81,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,客席にいるのは雪だるまだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.07,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,頑張りな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.32,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.82,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ということで　いよいよ本番が始まる
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.79,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,今日のライブは
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.79,0:10:01.46,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,私たちがもっと遠くまで行くための第一歩
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.83,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あなたたちはすごいアイドルになって
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.21,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,世界を変える
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.68,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ワンスー
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.34,main-JP,All,0,0,0,,モアモア
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.56,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,もっと大きく　ワンスー
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.43,main-JP,All,0,0,0,,モアモア
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.89,main-JP,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,ルルトリリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.19,0:10:35.70,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みんな　今日は目いっぱい楽しもうね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.88,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,{\an8}かわいいぞ！
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.23,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みんな　たのしんでくれだ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.07,0:11:17.49,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そんなにいっぱい応援してくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,配信を見てるファンのみんなも盛り上がってる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.71,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みんなの顔を見てたら
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.71,0:11:29.50,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私アイドルになったんだなって思った
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.92,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,きっと見てくれてるよね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.46,0:11:37.09,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,今日は大切なあなたのために歌うね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.01,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,次はルルちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.43,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.77,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私の大好きな友達で
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.02,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルトリリィのパートナー
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.27,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,よ、よろひくお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,可愛いなぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.03,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,歌って
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.82,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.37,main-JP,Shota,0,0,0,,やばあ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.10,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,2人とも頑張れ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.23,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.86,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ルルのパート終わったから　いよいよだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.03,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.08,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,なんか　これ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.04,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,大丈夫かな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.08,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ダメでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.21,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,えぇ　それならさっき言ってよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.13,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,いやでも　塔子がやりたいんだろうなって
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.05,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,うわやっぱりダメだ　このトロッコしょぼい
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.59,main-JP,Seena,0,0,0,,まぁ　みんなで作ったんだし
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.55,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,戻りました
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.39,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,2人ともちょっと聞いて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.64,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,トロッコのルートが変更になった
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.73,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.69,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ちょっと会場の都合で
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.03,main-JP,Staff 2,0,0,0,,トロッコを出します　スタンバイお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.94,main-JP,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.45,main-JP,Staff 2/3,0,0,0,,いきます
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.74,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ごめん　行ってきて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.70,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やっほー　楽し…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.92,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,皆　元気
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.50,main-JP,Mizuka,0,0,0,,これだけ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.59,main-JP,Momo,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.47,main-JP,Hisashi,0,0,0,,だ　だぜ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.73,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ああああ　こんなはつじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.35,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,やっぱすべったか
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.56,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,もっと盛り上がる予定が
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.65,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,歌が始まれば大丈夫でしょう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.65,0:13:57.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,だって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.78,main-JP,Staff 3,0,0,0,,トロッコ撤収します
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.40,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,落ち着こう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.41,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,みんなで作ったトロッコだもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.28,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ルルリラ　プルリラ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.87,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,もっと素敵なトロッコに変わって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.34,main-JP,Staff 2/3,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.31,0:14:31.60,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ラストは2人の新曲　一緒に歌うね
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.23,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,行くよー
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.16,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,世奈
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.78,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.99,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,やばり私
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.83,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ステージに立ちたい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.00,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,私も
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.13,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,楽しかったねえ　ルルちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.93,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい　二人一緒だったから怖くなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.47,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あー　終わっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.22,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もっともっとみんなと居たかったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.48,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,みなさんも楽しかったですか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.90,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やったー
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.98,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,よかったです
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.19,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,頑張ったもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.24,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,大変でした
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.82,0:16:51.37,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ワンスモアのみんなもすごい協力してくれたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.99,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,本当に皆さんのおかげです
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.79,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みんなに会えて嬉しかった
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.00,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ライブ大成功
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.92,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私今日のこと絶対忘れません
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.84,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,歌がもっと大好きになりました
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.71,0:17:12.01,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルとリリィのこと　これからもよろしく
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.85,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,よろしくお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.64,main-JP,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.64,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,決めた
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.03,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんか　寝れない
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.20,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,まだドキドキしてる
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,終わった気がしないな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.16,0:18:24.67,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,魔法を初めて使った時も　夢みたいって思ったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.92,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,今日のライブも夢みたいだった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.17,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす　今日私どうだった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.43,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ねぇねぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.55,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,どうでもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.93,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,こいつめ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.14,0:18:42.93,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,寒い
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.98,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,今日　楽しかったな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.11,0:18:53.65,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私ね　変身したらみんなの前で歌えたんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.62,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの日　リリィさんの歌に背中を押されて
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.87,0:19:05.04,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私の歌　みんな喜んでくれてた
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.96,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,夢みたい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.84,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,流　寒いよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.80,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あっごめんね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.44,0:19:29.36,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.23,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.11,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.15,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,早いね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.70,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,風こそ　珍しいね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.70,0:19:39.12,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん　なんか起きちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.16,0:19:46.37,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あのね　私昨日ね　いいことがあって
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.13,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.00,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ううん　なんでもない
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.51,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,今日あったかそう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.26,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.80,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お散歩でも行こうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.76,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私も行く
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.14,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん早く
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.14,0:20:06.89,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.28,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,気持ちいい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.03,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん　楽しそうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.87,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もしかして　何かいいことあった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.29,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そうなのわかる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,わぁやっぱり　そうだと思ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.55,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ねえねえ　教えて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.84,0:20:40.22,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,昨日　空を飛ぶ夢見ちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.68,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あのね　私も一緒なの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.77,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,風も
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.48,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.10,0:20:51.23,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そっか　お姉ちゃんも私と同じだったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.99,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.83,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,考えてもなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.79,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私以外に魔法を使う人がいたなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.79,0:21:18.26,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私ね　実は魔法が使えるの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.63,0:21:24.72,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私ね　実は魔法が使えるの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.89,0:21:26.93,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.31,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.02,0:21:31.60,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,この前見かけて可愛かったから
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.81,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんにも一個あげる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.07,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,2個セットだったの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.24,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いつも通りにやれば大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リラックスリラックス
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.67,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お星さまにのった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.67,0:22:02.34,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ふわふわの雲が
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.68,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そうだ　これ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.69,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,子供の頃の
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.82,0:22:19.44,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,二人の歌
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.53,0:22:23.66,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,風は
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.53,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,もしかして
Comment: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:29.51,main-CN,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.26,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,风已经起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.31,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.06,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,啊 一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.07,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,舞台很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.07,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,嗯 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.82,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,尽情歌唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.12,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:03.96,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.10,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.35,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,会迟到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:21.14,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不会 没事 我早起了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:26.15,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,姐姐她 会不会看演唱会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:27.73,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:30.82,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,毕竟她是莉莉的粉丝 还有现场直播呢
Comment: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.43,main-CN,,0,0,0,,main
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.06,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,没有人在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.10,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,黛特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.10,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.90,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,就这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.32,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,这不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.21,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,帕姆帕姆力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.34,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,露露莉菈 蒲露莉菈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.01,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,啵硼帕姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.33,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,走吧 红豆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:31.88,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.00,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,好危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.47,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,这是「露露与莉莉」第一次演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.59,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.26,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,票都卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.68,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.72,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,我也是第一次看演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.97,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.73,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,初中生来看没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.14,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.15,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,篮球社角谷同学他们 也说要来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.65,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,那个人好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.03,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,狂热的粉丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.41,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.99,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,变装完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.50,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,我也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,快看豌豆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.75,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好多观众都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.21,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,感觉像是艺人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.63,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,真是嚣张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.88,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,应该还有露露的粉丝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.18,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:25.76,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.94,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.57,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,来 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.44,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.90,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,诶呀 没想到那两人竟然成组合了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.07,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.87,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,是啊 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:48.24,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,简直是完美的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.71,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,喂 别这么大声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.29,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,喂喂 你不是很期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.55,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,也 有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.17,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,骗人 明明你非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.51,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,还说昨天晚上根本睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.89,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,我没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.97,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,诶 翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.56,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,所以 你站那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.73,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,我是说「露露与莉莉」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:16.06,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,莉莉和莉莉 你喜欢哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.90,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,果然还是收到签名的莉莉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.94,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,不是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.99,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,难不成是成熟的露露更好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.37,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,都说了 那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.58,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,选哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.16,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.62,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,露 露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.54,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,请多多支持哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.13,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,露露露露露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.51,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.10,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.77,main-CN,Staff 1,0,0,0,,莉莉小姐 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.56,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.27,main-CN,Staff 2/3,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.82,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,早啊 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.24,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.66,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.95,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:09.74,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.75,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊社长 贵宾席上的名单你看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:17.00,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,哦 我看了 等会去打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.13,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,露露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.38,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,已经在准备室了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.34,main-CN,Staff 4,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.93,main-CN,Staff 4,0,0,0,,那个花车 真的要登台吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.64,main-CN,Staff 5,0,0,0,,今天观众席太满了 移动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.60,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,这点请想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.31,main-CN,Staff 4,0,0,0,,不过 我们的确有想过预备方案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.64,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.56,main-CN,Staff 5,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.86,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嘛 确实有点勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,哇 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.94,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.57,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯 马卡龙 我一直想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.74,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.70,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.96,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.96,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,肯定很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.22,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.18,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.93,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这个 好像是社长送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.72,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,诶好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.98,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好好吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.39,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.98,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,紧张缓解了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.73,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉能笑出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:29.41,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,直到刚才 脸颊还一直在抽搐 表情几乎垮掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.70,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好想看看露露垮掉的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.41,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,感觉是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:42.50,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,和平常一样就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.55,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,放松 放松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.51,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.02,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,这首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.06,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,两位 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.77,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.03,main-CN,Staff 3,0,0,0,,表演即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.66,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,哇 好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.95,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,满人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.54,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好强好强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.54,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,在这么多人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.96,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,接下来只要全心表演就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.34,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,至今为止大家都很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:25.96,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.46,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.17,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,炸翻全场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.47,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:34.80,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.76,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,你的歌声很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.39,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,要有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.56,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.81,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,观众席上的都是雪人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.07,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.32,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.82,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,总之就是这样 终于到正式表演了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.79,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,今天的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:01.46,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,是让我们能走得更远的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.83,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,你们要成为厉害的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.21,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,去改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.68,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,再次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.34,main-CN,All,0,0,0,,闪耀闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.56,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,再大声一点 再次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.43,main-CN,All,0,0,0,,闪耀闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.89,main-CN,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,露露与莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:35.70,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,大家 今天要尽情享受呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.88,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,{\an8}超级可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.23,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,大家 开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:17.49,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,谢谢大家这么多的应援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,直播看的粉丝们 有嗨起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.71,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,看到大家的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:29.50,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我就觉得自己真的成为偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.92,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你肯定也在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:37.09,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,今天我会为了最重要的你而歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.01,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,接下来是露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.43,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.77,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.02,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,「露露与莉莉」的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.27,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,大 大家多说指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.03,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,歌唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.82,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.37,main-CN,Shota,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.10,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,两位都要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.23,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.86,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,露露的环节结束 是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.03,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.08,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,感觉 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.04,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.08,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.21,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,诶 要这样的话你不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.13,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,不是 看你很想用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.05,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊 果然不行啊 这个花车太寒碜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.59,main-CN,Seena,0,0,0,,算啦 毕竟是大家一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.55,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.39,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,两位听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.64,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,花车的路线要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.73,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.69,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,因为场地太窄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.03,main-CN,Staff 2,0,0,0,,花车准备出发 请做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.94,main-CN,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.45,main-CN,Staff 2/3,0,0,0,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.74,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,抱歉 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.70,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,哟吼 开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.92,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,大家 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.50,main-CN,Mizuka,0,0,0,,就这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.59,main-CN,Momo,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.47,main-CN,Hisashi,0,0,0,,好 好菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.73,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊啊啊啊 根本不是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.35,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,果然冷场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.56,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,我还想让气氛更加劲爆的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.65,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,只要开始歌唱就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:57.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.78,main-CN,Staff 3,0,0,0,,开始撤走花车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.40,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.41,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,毕竟是大家一起做的花车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.28,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,露露莉菈 蒲露莉菈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.87,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,让花车变得更加华丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.34,main-CN,Staff 2/3,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:31.60,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,最后是两人的新歌 要一起唱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.23,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.16,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,世奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.78,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.99,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,果然我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.83,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,还想站上舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.00,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.13,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,很开心呢 露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.93,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是的 因为两人一起表演就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.47,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.22,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好想再和大家多待一会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.48,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,大家也是开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.90,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.98,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.19,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,毕竟很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.24,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:51.37,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,再次闪耀的大家 也给予了很多支持
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.99,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,真的多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.79,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,能够与大家见面我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.00,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,演唱会大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.92,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我不会忘记今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.84,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我变得更加喜欢唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:12.01,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,今后也要多多支持「露露与莉莉」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.85,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.64,main-CN,Fuu/Rui,0,0,0,,谢谢观看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.64,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.03,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,总感觉 睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.20,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,还是心在砰砰跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,一种还没结束的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:24.67,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,第一次使用魔法的时候 感觉就像在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.92,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,但今天的演唱会更像是一场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.17,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆 今天的我怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.43,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.55,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,怎样都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.93,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:42.93,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.98,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,今天好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:53.65,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我啊 变身之后在大家面前唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.62,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那天 是莉莉的歌曲推了我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:05.04,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我的歌 也让大家开心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.96,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,就像梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.84,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,流 我好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.80,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,啊对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:29.36,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.23,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.11,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.15,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,起好早呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.70,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,风也是 好少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:39.12,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯 睡着睡着就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:46.37,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个 我昨晚 发生了件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.13,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.00,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.51,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,今天很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.26,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.80,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,要不要出去散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.76,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.14,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,姐姐快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:06.89,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.28,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.03,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,姐姐看起来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.87,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,难不成 发生了什么好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.29,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,这样看得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,哇真的吗 我就这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.55,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,呐呐 告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:40.22,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,昨晚 梦见自己在天空飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.68,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那个 我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.77,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,风也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.48,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:51.23,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这样啊 姐姐也和我一样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.99,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.83,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我从未想过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.79,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,除了我之外还有能够使用魔法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:18.26,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我呀 实际上会使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:24.72,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我呀 实际上会使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:26.93,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.31,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:31.60,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,之前看到非常可爱就买了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.81,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,也给姐姐一个用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.07,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,因为两个是一组的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.24,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,和平常一样就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,放松放松
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.67,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,乘着星星飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:02.34,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,软软绵绵的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.68,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是啊 这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.69,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是我们小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:19.44,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,两个人作的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:23.66,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.53,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,难不成是…
